OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy for many areas with
OL,6,Frain, especially across central and
OL,7,Fsouthern parts, turning heavier later.
OL,8,FFurther north, skies stay mostly
OL,9,Fcloudy, though Scotland and Northern
OL,10,FIreland see sunny spells and scattered
OL,11,Fshowers. Staying mild for the time of
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain clears eastwards across
OL,15,Fsouthern areas, leaving clearer skies.
OL,16,FFurther showers affect the far north
OL,17,Fand northwest, but much of northern UK
OL,18,Fstays dry, widespread frost, and
OL,19,Fpossible icy patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
