OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloud and rain slowly clear
OL,6,Fthe southeast through the morning,
OL,7,Fbrightening from the west. Western
OL,8,Fareas stay mostly bright, though sharp
OL,9,Fshowers affect the far north later.
